public boolean isSatelliteCertExpired()
Return whether the satellite certificate has expired or not. True signifies that the grace period is over and that we need to lock the satellite down

Returns:
true if cert has expired, false otherwise

isSatelliteCertInGracePeriod

public boolean isSatelliteCertInGracePeriod()
Return whether the satellite certificate is in a grace period or not. False will be returned if the grace period is over or if it has not begun.

Returns:
true if in grace period, false otherwise
